<typeStatus id="54A677E9FFE85F58E72EDDDAFB65F805" box="[1149,1237,2008,2030]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">holotype</typeStatus>
). Scale bars a–b 
<quantity id="4CE564AEFFE85F58E625DDDBFA18F805" box="[1398,1448,2009,2030]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" unit="cm" value="1.0">1 cm</quantity>
, c–d 10 μm. Photos a–b by A. Kovalenko, c–d by O. Morozova.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="DF6299C3FFE95F59E3DBD8A4FF42FD34" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6608473" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6608473" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6608473/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" startId="15.[136,229,678,700]" targetBox="[272,1323,214,636]" targetPageId="15">
